  "detailed_description": "<i>Swingy Sword</i> is a casual 3D fighting game where you fight to the death against up to 4 of your friends in 6 unique game modes. The main goal of <i>Swingy Sword</i> is to make the controls as challenging as possible while still being exciting to play. <br>          <strong>Example: You use the 2 joysticks to move the legs individually and to swing your sword you press and hold one of the bumpers and press the D-Pad in the direction you want to swing.</strong><br>          If you like party games and you like games with Octodad style controls, you'll love <i>Swingy Sword</i>.",
  "about_the_game": "<i>Swingy Sword</i> is a casual 3D fighting game where you fight to the death against up to 4 of your friends in 6 unique game modes. The main goal of <i>Swingy Sword</i> is to make the controls as challenging as possible while still being exciting to play. <br>          <strong>Example: You use the 2 joysticks to move the legs individually and to swing your sword you press and hold one of the bumpers and press the D-Pad in the direction you want to swing.</strong><br>          If you like party games and you like games with Octodad style controls, you'll love <i>Swingy Sword</i>.",
